fields.name: Inception Perfume Oil Elixir 2ml
fields.description: Luxurious touch, pocket-sized bliss: Our 5ml Perfume Oil Elixir packs a powerful punch of oriental fragrance. Fresh top notes dance with a powdery, musky heart and settle into a woody embrace. Enjoy a long-lasting scent on the go, with a healthier alternative that pampers your skin and exudes instant luxury.

fields.name: Inception Perfume Oil Elixir 5ml
fields.description: Ditch the bulk, embrace the perfume revolution: Experience long-lasting fragrance and pampered skin with our 5ml Perfume Oil Elixir. This oriental masterpiece unfolds with fresh top notes, a powdery & musky heart, and a woody base. Tuck it in your bag for on-the-go luxury and enjoy the healthier alternative to traditional perfumes.

fields.name: Inception Perfume Oil Elixir 10ml
fields.description: Unleash a pocketful of luxury: Our concentrated 10ml Perfume Oil Elixir offers a scent that lingers. Fresh top notes give way to a powdery, musky heart and end with a woody embrace. Healthy for your skin and perfect for on-the-go touch-ups, this oriental magic will keep you feeling confident and captivating.

fields.name: Inception Beard Oil 30ml
fields.description: Bid farewell to patchy, dry beards. Our oil promotes thicker, healthier growth. Packed with Vitamin E and Omega-3, it deeply nourishes and softens beard hair, while keeping the skin underneath comfortable and moisturized. Indulge in the captivating scent experience, lasting for hours: crisp top notes, a warm and sensual heart, and a rich, woody base.
fields.ingredients: Coconut Oil, Jojoba Oil, Argan Oil, Vitamin E, Essential Oils

fields.name: Inception Body Oil 30ml
fields.description: Indulge in a moment of tranquility with our nourishing body oil. Coconut Oil and Vitamin E pamper your skin, leaving it deeply moisturized and soothed. Its calming anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties help protect against damage and reduce signs of aging. The enchanting scent unfolds like a story: fresh top notes dance with a powdery and musky heart, settling into an ambery and woody base.
fields.ingredients: Coconut Oil, Vitamin E, Essential Oils

fields.name: Inception Body Lotion 250ml
fields.description: Melt away stress and discover luxurious hydration with our silky body lotion. Enriched with nourishing ingredients and antioxidant Vitamin E, it wraps your skin in a comforting blend of moisture and softness. Immerse yourself in the captivating scent: sparkling top notes, a warm and powdery heart, and an earthy, woody base.
fields.ingredients: Aqua, Stearic Acid, C12-15 Alkyl Benzoate, Cetyl Alcohol, Sorbitol, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil, Olus Oil, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Dimethicone, Glycol Cetearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate, Magnesium Aluminum Silicate, Carbomer , Sodium Hydroxide, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenoxyethanol, Essential Oils

fields.name: Inception Shower Cream 250ml
fields.description: Unwind and indulge in the rich, creamy lather of our shower cream. Formulated with gentle cleansers and nourishing ingredients like Vitamin E, it cleanses and hydrates in one, leaving your skin feeling refreshed, pampered, and delicately scented. Immerse yourself in the captivating fragrance: sparkling top notes, a warm and powdery heart, and an earthy, woody base.
fields.ingredients: Aqua, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Decyl Glucoside, Phenoxyethanol, Olive Oil PEG-7 Esters, Glycerin, Glycol Distearate, Laureth-4, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Tocopheryl Acetate, Benzoic Acid, Citric Acid, Dehydroacetic Acid, Formic Acid, Essential Oils

fields.name: Inception Cream Soap 250ml
fields.description: Transform your handwashing routine into a sensory escape with our cream soap. Indulge in its rich lather as the captivating scent unfolds: a burst of freshness and invigoration that transitions into a captivatingly musky and earthy warmth. Enjoy clean, soft, and moisturized hands with every wash.
fields.ingredients: Aqua, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Glycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Glycol Distearate, C12-13 Alkyl Lactate, Laureth-4, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Citric Acid, Benzoic Acid, Dehydroacetic Acid, Formic Acid, Essential Oils
